data.description: Welcome to Inverness Point where location meets Lake Living Lifestyle.  This small, gated community offers a private marina in a very deep cove that currently has water(10/25/23).  You can enjoy the lake lifestyle w/your boat or jet ski is still floating less than .5 miles from your home.  This is RARE!  The tucked away, private neighborhood is only minutes from an elementary, a winery, a grocery store and lots of restaurants.   Don't miss this opportunity to own a newer, custom home in a highly desirable neighborhood that enjoys an extremely low tax rate of 1.7%  Neighborhood Information:  https://www.invernesspointatx.com
